<item>
            <title>[LU-3799] Interop 2.1.5&lt;-&gt;2.5 failure on test suite replay-single test_0d: mount fails</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3799</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/71cd2a80-06df-11e3-87de-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/71cd2a80-06df-11e3-87de-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_0d failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mount fails&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test log shows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Started lustre-MDT0000
Starting client: client-23-ib.lab.whamcloud.com: -o user_xattr,acl,flock client-20-ib@o2ib:/lustre /mnt/lustre
CMD: client-23-ib.lab.whamcloud.com mkdir -p /mnt/lustre
CMD: client-23-ib.lab.whamcloud.com mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,acl,flock client-20-ib@o2ib:/lustre /mnt/lustre
mount.lustre: according to /etc/mtab client-20-ib@o2ib:/lustre is already mounted on /mnt/lustre
 replay-single test_0d: @@@@@@ FAIL: mount fails 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment>server: lustre-master build #1617&lt;br/&gt;
client: 2.1.5</environment>
        <key id="20512">LU-3799</key>
